    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but isnt it kinda reckless to just keep spending like that if the debt is already huge? wont that just ruin the economy for everyone in the long run? feels like ignoring the debt is just avoiding a massive problem.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
