    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i get the \"balanced\" thing but u basically said the debt is just a symptom of not spending enough. isn't that a bit of a stretch? if a person just kept spending way more than they made, people would say they're being irresponsible, not \"investing in themselves.\" why is it different for a gov?",
